  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>General</Type>
    <Text>There is an outdoor heated pool at the hotel. The hotel is also close to Little Tokyo, Dodger Stadium, the University of Southern California (USC), Beverly Hills, Rodeo Drive, the Los Angeles Zoo &amp; Botanical Gardens and several California beaches. Disneyland is 48 miles (77.24 kms) from the hotel. (1007/CH)</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>SurroundingArea</Type>
    <Text>The hotel is conveniently located one mile from the Los Angeles Convention Center and the Staples Center,  near popular attractions like Hollywood, University of California, Los Angeles (UCLA), Chinatown Los Angeles and Universal Studios Hollywood. The Los Angeles International Airport (LAX) is 15 miles (24 kms) from the hotel.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>RoomTypes</Type>
    <Text>Spacious guest rooms with voice mail, iron/ironing boards and free HBO. Handicap accessible and non-smoking rooms are also available.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>PropertyInformation</Type>
    <Text>Three-story Mediterranean-style hotel.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>DiningFacilities</Type>
    <Text>There is no on-site restaurant, but the hotel offers complimentary continental breakfast. There are a wide variety of restaurants and cocktail lounges located in the surrounding area.</Text>
